data.description: Welcome to your spacious retreat in the heart of Stone Mountain! This beautifully maintained 4 bedroom, 2 full bath room and half bath home offers ample space and comfort for the whole family. Featuring a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a cozy living room with a electric wall mounted fireplace, and a lush backyard perfect for outdoor gatherings. Located in a desirable neighborhood, close to parks, schools, and shopping. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home!"
